title: The Goons Of Doom and Ozzie Wright in Byron Bay
description:
Electric Visual and Volcom bring you the GOONS OF DOOM playing live in the new Volcom store in Byron Bay! Ozzie hung around for a few days and scored some waves with our young grom Kyuss King. 

Music: Goons of Doom - Billie Lee
Film and Edit: Gabe Roxburgh
